        <abstract>
            <p>Supports idea to translate C. K. Sprengel, but opposes publishing it together with H. Müller because this would raise price of Müller’s useful book.</p>
            <p>Confirms JDH’s observation that only tip of cabbage radicle shows geotropism.</p>
